<p>TrueCar Trade is a newer product offering from TrueCar, and there are specific guidelines in how we message trade to differentiate ourselves from the competition.</p>

<h2>Consumer Facing Version</h2>

<p>TrueCar Trade is the new, better way to sell or trade-in your car. With TrueCar Trade, consumers receive the most transparent and accurate real-time valuation of their car in minutes, based on their car&rsquo;s unique condition. This specific, third-party backed value is sent in minutes in the form of a True Cash Offer, which the consumer can take to their TrueCar Certified Dealer of choice for a side-by-side check before cashing out or trading their car in for a new or used one.</p>

<h2>Dealer Facing Version</h2>

<p>TrueCar Trade is a new product that is modernizing the retail and wholesale marketplace. Dealers can now offer a transparent, mobile, and 3rd party validated experience for consumers ready to sell or trade-in their car. Using a real-time, 17-digit accurate VIN algorithm, TrueCar Trade offers consumers the most accurate valuation in the industry, earning their trust. And once the transaction is completed, Dealers have a 48-hour remarketing guarantee, so they have the option to keep what they want and sell what they don&rsquo;t.</p>

<h2>Corporate Version</h2>

<p>TrueCar Trade is a next generation platform designed to serve as a transparent, mobile friendly experience for both Dealers and consumers. Powered by Galves Market Data, TrueCar Trade provides consumers with a transparent, real-time valuation of their car, enabling Dealers to build greater trust with consumers. The TrueCar Trade platform is designed to serve as a modern, leading-edge tool for consumers and a cost-effective, best-in-class acquisition tool for Dealers.</p>

